---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import NewsletterForm from '../components/NewsletterForm.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Speaking — David Henzel"
  description="Book David Henzel to speak at your event. Topics include conscious leadership, the Love Not Fear operating system, AI + entrepreneurship, and self-leadership systems."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-12">
      <div class="max-w-xl">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-secondary/60 mb-4">Speaking</p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground mb-5 leading-tight">
          Book David to Speak
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-8">
          I speak about conscious leadership, building companies from a place of love, and the systems that help people find their purpose. Whether it's a keynote, workshop, webinar, podcast, or university lecture — I bring real stories from 25+ years of building.
        </p>
        <a
          href="mailto:dh@davidhenzel.com?subject=Speaking%20Inquiry"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-accent text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-accent/90 transition-colors"
        >
          Get in touch
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="shrink-0">
        <img
          src="/images/david-onstage.png"
          alt="David Henzel speaking on stage"
          class="w-56 h-56 md:w-72 md:h-72 rounded-xl object-cover border border-border"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Talk Topics -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 border-t border-border">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground mb-10">Talk Topics</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="p-6 border border-border rounded-xl bg-background">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Love Not Fear: The Operating System for Conscious Leadership</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          How to make better decisions by understanding the two forces that drive every choice — and building systems that keep you operating from love.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 border border-border rounded-xl bg-background">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0114.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0112 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">From Introvert to CEO: Building Companies from a Place of Love</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          The personal story of a self-described recovering introvert who built and sold multiple companies — and how self-awareness became his greatest competitive advantage.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 border border-border rounded-xl bg-background">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904L9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 003.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 003.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09 3.09zM18.259 8.715L18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 002.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 002.455 2.456L21.75 6l-1.036.259a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.455 2.456zM16.894 20.567L16.5 21.75l-.394-1.183a2.25 2.25 0 00-1.423-1.423L13.5 18.75l1.183-.394a2.25 2.25 0 001.423-1.423l.394-1.183.394 1.183a2.25 2.25 0 001.423 1.423l1.183.394-1.183.394a2.25 2.25 0 00-1.423 1.423z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">AI + Entrepreneurship: Building the Future Without Losing Your Soul</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          How AI is reshaping entrepreneurship, and why the founders who will win are the ones who stay human-centered in an increasingly automated world.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 border border-border rounded-xl bg-background">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 3v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 006 16.5h2.25M3.75 3h-1.5m1.5 0h16.5m0 0h1.5m-1.5 0v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 0118 16.5h-2.25m-7.5 0h7.5m-7.5 0l-1 3m8.5-3l1 3m0 0l.5 1.5m-.5-1.5h-9.5m0 0l-.5 1.5m.75-9l3-3 2.148 2.148A12.061 12.061 0 0116.5 7.605" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Self-Leadership Systems: Purpose, Values, Vision, Habits</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          A practical framework for getting clear on who you are, what you want, and how to build daily systems that move you toward it — the four pillars of the LNF operating system.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 border border-border rounded-xl bg-background md:col-span-2">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 003.741-.479 3 3 0 00-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198l.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0112 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 016 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 00-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0012 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 00-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 00-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 003.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 00-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Love Not Fear Workshops: Interactive Team Sessions</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Half-day or full-day workshops for teams and organizations. Participants discover their purpose, define their values, and build personal operating systems — creating alignment from the inside out.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Past Appearances -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 border-t border-border">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground mb-6">Past Appearances</h2>
    <p class="text-base text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-2xl">
      Keynotes, panels, and podcasts on entrepreneurship, conscious leadership, and self-leadership systems.
    </p>
    <ul class="space-y-3 max-w-2xl">
      {[
        'Forbes Business Council — Guest Contributor',
        'YEC (Young Entrepreneur Council) — Member & Speaker',
        'Running Remote — Future of Distributed Teams',
        'SaaS Talk — Building Companies with Purpose',
        'The Startup Chat Podcast — Multiple Appearances',
        'Kyle Gray Show Podcast — Love Not Fear Framework',
        'University guest lectures — Self-Leadership for Students',
        'Corporate workshops & webinars — Love Not Fear for Teams',
      ].map((item) => (
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-secondary">
          <span class="shrink-0 mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent/60"></span>
          {item}
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 border-t border-border">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground mb-4">
        Interested in having David speak?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
        I'm available for keynotes, workshops, webinars, podcasts, and university lectures. Reach out and let's make it happen.
      </p>
      <a
        href="mailto:dh@davidhenzel.com?subject=Speaking%20Inquiry"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-foreground text-background text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-foreground/85 transition-colors"
      >
        dh@davidhenzel.com
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
